<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Excellent addition to a limited repetiore of the Rogue Class.  Was given one of these by a friendly gnome, Igbot, and do enjoy it's use.  The only problem is that in long battles, you need to watch that stamina bar.  The Harpoon is heavy, 6.5 compared to the Burning Rapier and Serrated Bone Dirk, which is the staple of the Rogue's weapons from 25-40 or so.<BR>
<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
